name: Pull Ups
description: The pull up is a lower body excercise for your back but it also works out your upper back.
extra: Lie Down. Sit at the end of your flat bench first. Squeeze Your Shoulder-blades. Raise your chest and tighten your upper-back.Grab The Bar. Pinky inside the ring marks.Set Your Feet. Feet flat on the floor using a shoulder-width stance.Unrack. Straighten your arms to lift the bar out of the uprights.
